CHINESE CHECKERS, V 1.4, 8-1-92, animated
graphics board game for 1-6 players.  The
players (represented by animated icons, a
Dragon, Wind, Flower, Mantis, Tiger, and
Peacock) can be played either by people or
the computer.  Use the keyboard or Microsoft
compatible mouse.  Requires EGA or VGA, and
640K of memory.  Nominated for Best Enter-
tainment Software at SSS 1992.  Developed by
ImagiSOFT, Inc. who is an ASP member.
